@node "9" "History"

History:
~~~~~~~~

V1-Versions:
~~~~~~~~~~~~
V1.0 (02.08.1997) - First Version ! Not released ! Only for internal
		    testings.
V1.1ß1 (02.08.97) - Fixed many bugs. Added the "About" Window. Not released.
V1.1ß2 (03.08.97) - Again Bugfixing. Optimized the Program for more speed !
		    Not released !
V1.1ß3 (06.08.97) - cP!_ShowConfig shows now ALL your external Boards
		    correctly !! A B-I-G Thanks to Sascha Reissner !!
		    Not released !
V1.1 (06.08.1997) - First released Version on Aminet !
		    I hope it works correctly ! :)
V1.2ß1 (13.08.97) - Added a "Save-Routine" that saves your system-
		    configuration to a file in ram: called cP!_Showconfig.txt
		    Fixed a few bugs. Added a Init-Routine for
		    rexxidentify.library, that future versions of
		    rexxidentify.library works with cP!_ShowConfig !
		    Added more nice Stuff about your System !
		    Fixed the Save-Routine for a bit more speed :)
V1.2ß2 (14.08.97) - Fixed a very damn bug ! Now cP!_ShowConfig works
		    100% correct (I hope) ;-) !
V1.2ß3 (18.08.97) - Added a "simple just for fun" Keyfile Routine.
		    If you would like have a personal Keyfile, just write
		    me ! Changed my EMail Address.. note:
		    campino@innocent.com is still active !
V1.2 (23.08.1997) - Added a little "Nerv-Requester" if you have no
                    cP!_ShowConfig Keyfile !
		    Released on Aminet !
V1.3ß1 (30.08.97) - Changed the "external-boards" routine. You have now
		    a new Output :)). If Last Alert = FFFFFFFF then
		    cP!_ShowConfig displays "No Alert yet... :)" !
V1.3 (14.09.1997) - Removed the Beta-Requester. Optimized the Mainprg.
		    Released on Aminet.
		    This is the last V1 Version !
V2-Versions:
~~~~~~~~~~~~
V2.0 (18.10.1997) - cP!_ShowConfig V2.0 is COMPLETLY rewritten !
		    Removed (rexx)identify.library support for version <4
		    Added moooooore functions (etc. AHI Version,
		    Commodities and much more !!), cP!_ShowConfig
		    closes the opened library's now.
		    It's too much to write, just check it out !!
		    Released on Aminet.
V2.1ß1 (28.10.97) - Fixed a little Bug in the Memory-Routine.
		    Support now for rexxextreq.library in the
		    Commodities Window !
V2.1ß2 (20.12.97) - Added cP!_ShowSystem to cP!_ShowConfig.
		    Fixed little Bug in cP!_ShowConfig.
V2.1ß3 (21.12.97) - Fixed a little (lame) bug in cP!_ShowConfig.
		    When you've installed the german catalog files from
		    (rexx)identify.library the "Clock" Output was
		    GERMAN, but cP!_ShowConfig has searched for the
		    ENGLISH Output. Now both Outputs are working !
		    Cleaned up the source a little bit :)
		    cP!_ShowConfig/cP!_ShowSystem gives now a little
		    Warn-Message to you, if you don't have a needed
		    Utility (c:list, c:delete ... etc) !
		    -=* INTERNAL TEST VERSION ONLY ! *=-
V2.1ß4 (21.12.97) - Added a new function to LastAlert. You can now see
		    what this LastAlert Code is.
		    Changed the Startup-Text in cP!_ShowSystem a LITTLE bit.
V2.1ß4a (21.12.97)- Forgot to add the Last-Alert analysing into the
		    Save-Routine ! :(
		    Changed the Labels from the LastAlert Analysing !
		    Now it's easier to understand what cP!_ShowConfig
		    means :)
V2.1ß5 (24.12.97) - Added support for the new (rexx)identify.library !
		    Both Libs included ! Now cP!_ShowConfig displays the
		    speed of the CPU (MHZ), CPU Revision and MUCH more !
		    You can now see the speed of your Ram etc. Check out
		    the MEM-Page !
		    THIS IS A FAST UPDATE TO THE BETATESTERS OF
		    CP!_SHOWCONFIG ! <- LIKE A X-MAS PRESENT !! :)))))
V2.1ß5a (25.12.97)- Flemming Steffensen found a bug: If LastAlert=No
		    Alert Yet, the Last-Alert Analyse bugged and shows
		    the variables (XA..) ! Changed the Title of
		    Clock to BATTCLOCK and changed a other little
		    Cosmetic-Stuff :))
		    ß5a specially for Flemming !
V2.1 (01.01.1998) - Changed a little bit the Guide ! :)
		    "Optimized" the Guide (Replaced spaces into tabs...)
		    Cleaned up the Source from cP!_ShowConfig.
		    Fixed some little cosmetic-bugs !
		    Copyright set to 1998 .. etc...
		    Released on Aminet !
V2.2ß1 (04.01.98) - cP!_ShowSystem: c:echo is not needed anymore !
		    I wrote a little Routine, to replace c:echo !
		    cP!_ShowConfig: little cosmetic-stuff changed !
		    e.g. if you have no FPU, cP!_SC displayed 0 MHz !
		    Now cP!_SC displays "None" ! ....
V2.2ß2 (24.01.98) - Added "Agnus", "Agnus Mode", "PPC OS" and "TCP/IP"-Stack,
		    if used.
V2.2ß3 (25.01.98) - cP!_ShowSystem: Now cP!_ShowSystem sorts the
		    Output by alphabetic !
V2.2ß3a (29.01.98)- cP!_ShowSystem: Now cP!_ShowSystem uses "c:DoVer"
		    instead of "c:version" !
		    Special Version to: Bill Duxbury !
V2.2ß4 (29.01.98) - V2.2ß3a works great and has fixed the "libs"-bug in
		    cP!_ShowSystem ! Optimized cP!_ShowConfig (gained
		    a few bytes :)) and updated the Texts/Strings in
		    cP!_ShowConfig/cP!_ShowSystem AND cP!_ShowConfig.guide !
V2.2 (07.02.1998) - Ok, No Bugs in the Beta's found :)
		    Now releasing V2.2 to Aminet ! :)
V2.3ß1 (13.02.98) - Now fixed the "Last-Alert"-Scan Bug !!! ;)
		    Added RexxExtReq.Library V1.3 to Archive ! Thanx Mr_W !
		    Not released ! Only for internal testings !
V2.3ß2 (22.02.98) - Now you can copy the cP!_ShowConfig.key to "PROGDIR:"
		    That mean's you DON'T must copy the Keyfile to S: !
		    You can copy the Key in the Directory of cP!_ShowConfig !
		    Added CLI Output ! Simple type in a CLI:
		    cP!_ShowConfig.exe CLI and cP!_ShowConfig won't open
		    any window... -> Good for BBS's etc. !
V2.3ß3 (24.02.98) - Removed COMPLETE RexxReqtools-Code !
		    cP!_ShowConfig/cP!_ShowSystem uses now the BETTER,
		    more POWERFULL RexxExtReq.library ! Thanx again to
		    the coder, Mr_W !
		    This Version is a "ALPHA" Release. It can crash or
		    other things ! But I think it should work 99,9 % :)
V2.3ß4 (26.02.98) - Changed the look of the GUI like the wishes of the
		    users :) Optimized a little bit the Sourcecode.
		    Changed other GUI related things, now cP!_ShowConfig/
		    cP!_ShowSystem looks better :))
V2.3ß5 (29.03.98) - Added a space between the Text and the Border of the
		    window.
		    Fixed little thing: When cP!_ShowConfig was started
		    with Option "CLI" it has not deleted the Temp-Files
		    in T: -> Fixed ! (Now it deletes the Temp-Files).
		    Added Button "Run Exchange" in Commodities-Window !
		    You must have Exchange in sys:tools/commodities/ !
		    Added Tasks-Window to cP!_ShowSystem !
